data.description:
When you think of great neighborhoods in Broken Arrow, doesn't this one come to mind? First of all -- it has the notoriety and proximity to The Club at Forest Ridge. It's a beautiful golf course with a wonderful swimming pool. Serious about golf? You're 20 minutes from several other courses as well!

The house truly has a "baby bear" feel--It's just right! The master suite on this split floor plan is spacious. The laundry room connects to the master's large walk-in closet. The kitchen island gives you perfect position to prepare dinner while still being involved in movie night. The pantry and dining area give you more of the "just right" feelings. Down the street is access to 13 miles of local walking trails where you can experience beautiful sunrises! What about food, drink, and entertainment? We've got you covered! You are 10-15 minutes away from Charleston's, Crumbl Cookies, Andolini's, and much more. You're the same 10-15 minutes away from shopping and entertainment of The Rose District, Broken Arrow Hills, and Bass Pro Shop. You'll soon be 7 minutes away from your next pick up order at a brand new Walmart. Are you a Tiger? You're within 15 minutes of Broken Arrow High School and if proximity to Highland Park Elementary and Oneta Ridge Middle School is something you're interested in, you're definitely covered!
